summary:
some not depressing theories about why he's a bit skinnier and has slightly red eyes
weed. that's all I'm saying
exercise, guys...
body:
some not depressing theories about why he’s a bit skinnier and has slightly red eyes

  • weed. that’s all I’m saying
  • exercise, guys it’s been like,,,,, 4 months. he totally could have easily lost weight in a healthy way
  • some antidepressants make you gain weight and tbh, he could have gone off of them and therefore lost some of the weight
  • hes trying to go vegetarian/vegan which is so much healthier and doesnt make you gain as much weight

either way I feel likes he’s okay. he has phil to make sure everything is good, and even if it isnt romantic it’s obvious they love each other, so we can trust phil here. tbh I think we should just be there and understanding, not bombard dan with comments like “um u look sick” . there is no way that’s gonna help
